<source>The amount billed is the sum of the main item amount and any related adjustment item amounts.</source>
<seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">The amount billed is the sum of the main item amount and any related adjustment item amounts.</mrk></seg-source>
<target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">청구되는 금액은 주요 항목 금액과 그 밖의 관련된 모든 조정 항목 금액을 합한 금액입니다.</mrk></target></trans-unit>
